<br>
first i would like to say I have started and been playing an MA since the game launched in US, took a break for a while and then continued.  when i first started the MAs were absolutely the most horrible profession in game, after about lvl 60 you couldnt even solo a low green con. then came some nice changes and then some more. i have stuck with it pretty much through thick and thin and i was hoping that by time i hit 200 or at least TL6, the prof would be fixed to the point where i would be able to enjoy all aspects of teh game on at least a semi-decent level. but that is juts not the case. after all this time FC has decided to revert us to practical nothingness again at the upper levels.<br>
<br>
MAs overall are still great at newbie levels 1-50, and do ok below 120 and in PvM. And I also know and realize that there are a ton of people that say they dont PvP, or dont plan to , etc. But let me tell you this, you will want to in the longrun, and you will be very very dissapointed with your character unless FC makes some really drastic changes in our favor. By the same token I have learned that whatever FC fixes, they shortly break thereafter. To hope that FC will come up with some decent solutions is a waste.<br>
<br>
Also keep in mind that the game is becoming more and more PvP oriented, and PvP will now have serious rewards as well as consequences on the gameworld. Do you want to be the person taht at least has a chance of geting some of those rewards ? Or do you want to be the person that always gives the otehr side the points to earn theirs ? For those that have played DoAC there is a term the people in that game came out with that perfectly suits MAs: &quot;RP Cows&quot;.<br>
<br>
In light of all this, and the hopelessness with regards to any feasible practical solutions forthcoming from FC, I advice you to all quit MAs, start another profession that is more usefull. There  has been lots of testing done with his, and MAs now not only get completely owned in duels, but are utterly useless in team PvP as well. In fact, they are so bad now taht it is better to kick em out of group to be replaced with virtually any other prof.<br>
<br>
if you like to see the details on some of this, why is it so horrible, and what the numbers are, etc., feel free to visit the official MA board <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://forums.anarchy-online.com/forumdisplay.php?s=6b71099983a1eb9991b9d753d36a24e6&forumid=165">forums.anarchy-online.com...orumid=165</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> scroll down some pages if the posts arent on top. its all there.<br>
<br>
so please support our cause by sending e-mails to FC, or cancelling your account. if you are new, at least do yourself a favor and dont waste time on MA. play a doc enf or trader, we need more of those anyways in light of the 50% population being fixers lately and tradeskills coming more into play ahead of us.<br>
<br>
<br>
so see ya everyone<br>
<br>
