<br>
Now with that said, I will admit that the beta is probably not the best place to really determine how well MAs will do in massive PvP battles. Everyone in beta is lvl 200 with ql 200 imps, all prof nanos, and the best (and most rare) armor, weapons, and support gear available in the game. You won't see that everyday on Live Servers. BUT if MAs don't fare well in the most optimal setting that they can be in, how do you think they are gonna fare on the Live servers? Not well. See end sentence of first paragraph.<br>
<br>
